                "type": "text",
                "text": " ruining my image was definitely a concern from my time in Smalltalk.  Undo and some sensible process isolation go a long way.  Comfort comes from being able to answer: would clicking this break anything?  One fun dynamic way to tell is to speculatively execute the actions available from a given state recording their effects.  Then you can indicate which is which: does it change the view, the document, a broader model."
